      "body": "\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Gartner recently released their Critical Capabilities for Digital Commerce report, where 11 vendors were evaluated on products based on five critical capabilities and three use cases. And it is good, really good.<br />\nHybris Commerce has been named the leader for each use case, making it the best Commerce platform in the market today!</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p><br /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/RCEeZRpaAJW6Q85KgCy8gUxMrxE5y24WFDqCWI1BYDU=w550-h756-no\" alt=\"Promotion Banner\" /></p>\n\n<p><br /></p>\n\n<h1>Does that mean hybris consultants may be able to charge a higer rates? :-)</h1>\n\n"
